{"tid":409876,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【沉船】33歲港男1萬蚊叫雞  交易後女方唔肯拍拖遭勒索放裸照","createTime":"2017-09-22T12:16:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-22T14:20:26.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"03bbd079f30182aec904e3c34318313e8fd49cd6","tid":409876,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:16:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170921/photo/bkn-20170921180002805-0921_00822_001_01b.jpg?20170921201800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170921%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170921180002805-0921_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20170921201800&h=edd5cfc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n33歲男被告李德祥涉於本年5月，聲稱有一名妓女的裸照，並威嚇對方會在色情網站和討論區發布，勒索對方1萬港元。他否認一項刑事恐嚇和一項勒索罪，案件今(21日)於九龍城法院開審。<br />\n<br />\n事主X在屏風後作供，指和被告認識約1年半，被告是其顧客。於本年5月24日，被告過數1萬港元後，兩人到酒店進行性交易。事主原同意翌日早上一同食早餐，但被告「發脾氣」，又指「之後唔好再見」。事主遂離開，惟被告來電又要求一同食早餐，聲稱擁有對方的照片。事主大驚，遂到一間快餐店和被告見面，被告卻要求和事主拍拖，遭事主拒絕。事主離開後，收到被告的短訊，聲稱會把事主的照片上載至色情網站，她同日報警。<br />\n<br />\n庭上播放被告的錄影會面，他稱於去年6月到上環和事主進行性交易，兩人之後維持性工作者和嫖客的關係。於本年4月某一晚上，事主致電被告，兩人傾談7小時，話題包括事主的前度，和其性工作等，期間事主示愛，坦認對被告有意思。被告回應自己非好人，吩咐事主勿胡思亂想，事主則回應：「你唔鍾意我，但唔可以阻止我鍾意你」。他們之後再相約見面，被告表示可以「試吓一齊」。<br />\n<br />\n去年5月24日，兩人再相約性交，被告把1萬港元轉帳予事主後，兩人到酒店性交。翌日早上，被告打算再性交，惟見事主已穿回衣服，打算離開，因此感到不滿，兩人口角後離開酒店。被告指1萬港元是包括兩次性次，深深不忿下遂「諗住嚇吓佢」。他承認曾向事主稱擁有對方裸照，但實際上沒有。據悉，案中警方並沒有發現事主的裸照。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.titanicuniverse.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/10/titanic-sinking-underwater.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.titanicuniverse.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2009%2F10%2Ftitanic-sinking-underwater.jpg&h=1a502bc4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e723cf0b7777aad0b7e10e6c492512f810acf15c","tid":409876,"uid":81995,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:42:57.000Z","msg":"33 頭已經禿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53c1801386ad0b373955e9985507615cf705520e","tid":409876,"uid":52276,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:45:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>33 頭已經禿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n叫得雞多係咁&hellip;"},{"pid":"a33dbe2385dd7e531fe610c0b81e7268027827c2","tid":409876,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:46:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"64fbd4566e46e3f6afb8246a5568289ea638c515","tid":409876,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:48:08.000Z","msg":"嫖客柒<br />\n隻雞又唔識做"},{"pid":"5c6ad903d8ac09853bdf2bf6d3511dabd126be56","tid":409876,"uid":120955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:54:57.000Z","msg":"港女咁撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18010929718718eda65292bd0e4960fcb11f51bb","tid":409876,"uid":109602,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:55:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7506afcd548fc0b3249421f4109cfa11b3e2eac1","tid":409876,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:56:39.000Z","msg":"33歲<br />\nD頭髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d912bd9709e90b2319f96b5e730ed04847f0ec86","tid":409876,"uid":281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T13:00:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb62aa9496153919ac7769c64259f414d05f530a","tid":409876,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T13:16:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">newlife五毛起底</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/bzoe9k7q\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fbzoe9k7q&h=99ae6483&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/fgzy3w50\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ffgzy3w50&h=bf68cf95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7aa59869395d2f5456183cf591790bce4ca08